{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think this was the longest place we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And until one day, we had to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It took two months to resettle the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I found that out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I guess for two months, we were hiding from place to place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in-- in-- when we were in that, amongst these pipes, when I got out, my feet were all swollen because from the cold of the pipes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I could hardly move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we found another place, which was warm in a building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, somehow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my brother went out, and I guess he found work, and I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one day, I just-- I couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I tried to go find someplace else where there are some people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I-- I went out, and I went over to where they were working, and they were working-- some of them were working to plant-- plant things that we, in turn, I guess, later on, I found out, where we would eat-- eat those-- like, vegetables, or whatever they were planting, and it must have been early spring, because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were planting.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that's the only deduction I can make.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I tried to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I remember, I've seen some people from our camp, I've seen even the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And nobody tried to stop me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He asked me how old, and I said I want to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And somehow, he didn't stop me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He didn't-- he didn't turn me back, he didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But, pretty soon, somebody approached me and told me, I better get out of here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It could have been my brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It could have been my little brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
